## 3. دورة حياة الحزمة (Packet Lifecycle)

### 3.1 المخطط التسلسلي الكامل

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant NIC   as 🔌 Network Interface Card
    participant EBPF  as ⚡ eBPF / XDP Engine
    participant PROXY as 🔄 Transparent Proxy
    participant CTX   as 📦 Context Enricher
    participant PIPE  as 🔄 Inspection Pipeline
    participant MODS  as 🔍 DPI Modules (FW/WAF/DLP...)
    participant AI    as 🤖 Predictive AI
    participant NET   as 🌐 Internet

    NIC->>EBPF: Incoming Packet
    alt IP in Blocklist
        EBPF-->>NIC: XDP_DROP (Hardware Kill)
    else Pass
        EBPF->>PROXY: XDP_PASS
    end

    PROXY->>PROXY: iptables REDIRECT (Port 80→8080)
    PROXY->>CTX: Raw TCP Stream

    Note over CTX: Inject Identity (JWT/Device)<br/>Inject Risk Score (UBA)<br/>Inject Session Metadata (GeoIP)

    CTX->>PIPE: Enriched InspectionContext

    loop Per Module (sorted by Priority)
        PIPE->>MODS: inspect(context)
        MODS-->>PIPE: InspectionResult (ALLOW/DROP/score)
    end

    PIPE->>AI: Telemetry Meta-Data
    AI-->>EBPF: Block Signal (if threat correlated)

    alt All Modules → ALLOW
        PIPE->>PROXY: Forward to Internet
        PROXY->>NET: Egress (NAT Masquerade)
        NET-->>PROXY: Response
        PROXY-->>NIC: Response to Client
    else Any Module → DROP
        PIPE-->>NIC: 403 Block Page
    end
```

### 3.2 دورة حياة مبسّطة (Simplified Flow)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A([كابل الشبكة\nNIC]) --> B{eBPF\nFast-Path}
    B -->|محظور| Z([❌ XDP_DROP\nزمن: ~1µs])
    B -->|مسموح| C[Transparent Proxy\nاعتراض المرور]
    C --> D[Context Enricher\nإضافة الهوية والمخاطر]
    D --> E{Inspection\nPipeline}
    E --> F[🛡️ Firewall ACL]
    E --> G[🌐 WAF]
    E --> H[🦠 Malware AV]
    E --> I[📄 DLP]
    E --> J[🤖 Predictive AI]
    F & G & H & I & J --> K{القرار\nالنهائي}
    K -->|ALLOW| L([🌐 الإنترنت\nعبر NAT])
    K -->|DROP| M([🚫 صفحة الحظر])
```

