## 5. نموذج الهوية والتحقق (Zero-Trust Identity Model)

```mermaid
graph TD
    REQ["📨 HTTP Request\nIncoming"] --> AGG["🔀 Identity Aggregator"]
    
    subgraph "Identity Sources"
        JWT["🎫 JWT Token\n(jwt_enricher.py)"]
        DEV["💻 Device Fingerprint\n(device_enricher.py)"]
        UBA2["👤 UBA Behavioral Score\n(uba_enricher.py)"]
        GEO["🌍 GeoIP\n(session.py)"]
    end
    
    JWT --> AGG
    DEV --> AGG
    UBA2 --> AGG
    GEO --> AGG

    AGG --> CTX["📦 InspectionContext\n(Unified Identity Object)"]
    
    CTX --> EVAL{"Risk Evaluation"}
    EVAL -->|"Risk < 0.3"| LOW["✅ Full Access"]
    EVAL -->|"0.3 ≤ Risk < 0.7"| MED["⚠️ Limited Access\n+ Step-up Auth"]
    EVAL -->|"Risk ≥ 0.7"| HIGH["🚫 Block + Alert\n+ Quarantine"]
```

