## 9. محرك الارتباط التنبؤي (Correlation Engine)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Event Sources"
        DNS_E["🔍 DNS: Suspicious query\nScore = 30%"]
        FW_E["🛡️ Firewall: Unusual port\nScore = 30%"] 
        UBA_E["👤 UBA: Off-hours login\nScore = 30%"]
    end

    subgraph "system/core/correlation_engine"
        SINK["📥 Event Sink\n(telemetry/unified_sink.py)"]
        CORR["🧠 CorrelationEngine\ncorrelation_engine.py"]
        RULES["📋 Correlation Rules\nAPT Rule: DNS+FW+UBA → 90%"]
        WINDOW["⏱️ Time Window\n300 seconds memory"]
    end

    DNS_E & FW_E & UBA_E -->|"Emit TelemetryEvent"| SINK
    SINK --> CORR
    CORR --> RULES
    CORR --> WINDOW
    RULES -->|"Combined Score ≥ 0.85"| ALERT["🚨 Global Block\n+ Admin Alert\n+ eBPF Inject"]
```

