## 10. المُحسِّن الذكي (Smart Policy Optimizer) — المرحلة السادسة

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    ADMIN["👨‍💻 Admin Clicks:\n'Run Analysis'"] --> API2["GET /api/v1/optimizer/suggestions"]
    API2 --> OPT["🧮 FirewallOptimizer\n(system/firewall/optimizer.py)"]
    
    subgraph "Heuristic Algorithms (Deterministic)"
        S1["1️⃣ Shadow Rule Detection\n∀ rule_b: subnet(b) ⊆ subnet(a)\n→ rule_b never matches = delete"]
        S2["2️⃣ Dead Rule Eviction\nhit_count == 0\n→ suggest disable"]
        S3["3️⃣ Redundancy Merging\nSame dest+port+action\n→ merge into IP Group"]
    end

    OPT --> S1 & S2 & S3
    S1 & S2 & S3 --> REPORT["📋 Optimization Report\n{severity, reason, action}"]
    REPORT --> UI["🖥️ Optimizer.jsx\nInteractive Diff View"]
    UI -->|"Admin Accepts"| APPLY["POST /api/v1/optimizer/apply\n→ Update base.yaml\n→ Hot-Reload Engine"]
```

